The observations on Table 5 are given as follows.
The algorithm carefully examines the existence of feasible branches, eliminates unwanted branches with the help of effective bounding strategies.
The results indicate that the algorithm is capable to solve the higher dimension instances of TTP optimally within a reasonable computational time.
The solution of the algorithm highly influenced by the parametric values \documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
